12032 /******************************************************************************/
12033 /* For a painless codes migration between the STM32F3xx device product */
12034 /* lines, the aliases defined below are put in place to overcome the */
12035 /* differences in the interrupt handlers and IRQn definitions. */
12036 /* No need to update developed interrupt code when moving across */
12037 /* product lines within the same STM32F3 Family */
12038 /******************************************************************************/
12039
